PHPTaskManager is useful when you want to run some task periodically
and you don't want to hold their configuration outside your project
e.g. in system crontab file. 

Usage: php example.php crontab

For more info see example.php

http://dl.dropbox.com/u/275381/nowicki.cjb.net/index.html?php-task-manager

